    <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
      <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
          <p xml:id="Aink415-kilavi">ituvum atu.</p>
          <p xml:lang="en">And this is that.</p>
        </div>
        <div rend="parallel">
          <lg xml:id="Aink415">
<l>ituvē maṭantainā mēviya poḻutē</l>
<l>yutuvē maṭantainā muḷḷiya puṟavē</l>
<l>yiṉituṭaṉ kaḻikki liḷamai</l>
<l>yiṉitā lamma viṉiyavarp puṇarvē.</l>
          </lg>
          <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>This, young woman, is the time I desired.</l>
<l>And that, young woman, is the woodland I thought about.</l>
<l>An unwasted youth spent sweetly -</l>
<l>O, how sweet it is, the lovers' union.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </body>
    </text>
